4)class vs id? (html,css-code pathave puriyum)
        class->multiple selector(not unique)-neraya selector aa use pannalam but ithu unique aaa irukaathu(multiple code ku same color kudukarathuku use agum)
            (eg:entha code kulamm same color and vera changes kudukunum nu nenaikaramo athukulaam class kudukanum)
        
        
        id->unique selector(unique)-ithu unique aa onnu mattum thaan use pannuvom (ovoru code kum color thanithaniya add pannuvoom)
             (eg:entha code kulamm vera vera color and changes pannanum nu nenikuroomo athukulamm id kudukanum)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
