1)pseudo-classes:

   i)anchor tag link irunthuchuna athooda color mathunumna:(antha link nmba browsor la ithuvarikum visite pannala na mattum thaan ithu act agum)
      a:link{
          color:black;
       }
   ii)antha link click pannitta antha link color matharathuku
      a:visited{
          color:red;
        }

   iii)antha link thoda pogumboothu antha olor matha:
       a:hover{
         color:green;
        }

   iv)antha link click pannumboothu colora matharathuku:
      a:active{
         color:blue;
       }
